                        <support>
                           <p><material>Marble</material> <objectType>stele</objectType> consisting of a base carrying a nude figure of an athlete with 
                              a palm-branch in one hand and an unidentified object in the other, a group of objects, probably weights, beside him and a small altar 
                              on which lies an animal, perhaps a deer.</p>
                        </support>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
