         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>The portrait statue is dated by Rosenbaum, l.c., in the second quarter of third century; for the man see also <ref type="inscription">C94400</ref>.</p>
            <p> b. , line 2: Cf. Pausanias, I. 43.6 for a statue of Παρήγορος together with Πειθώ in the temple of Aphrodite Praxis at Megara, and Nonnus II. 205, XXXVI.386, for Νίκη Παρήγορος.</p>
         </div>
         
